title: SUPRA TWO FOR TUESDAY: Lizard King Costa Rica
description:
Lizard warms it up with a Front Nose then gets a bit creative at this crusty Costa Rican spot.

Two For Tuesday is our new weekly feature dropping every Tuesday on SupraSkateboarding.com and Instagram. It will consist of one trick two angles, one angle regular speed and a slo-mo, or just two tricks.
